WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Create a Python blog in 90 seconds

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Step 1. Open up VS Code and then Extensions

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Step 2. Add the Quarto extension

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Step 3. Open a new Quarto project

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Step 4. You have a new blog

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
Step 5. Open up the post and add your Python code

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Step 6. Create a new terminal

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:29.000
Step 7. Run Quarto preview and check out your new website

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:33.000
And just like that, you're done!

